text: Anapausa rugifrons is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1951. It is known from Papua New Guinea.BioLib.cz - Anapausa rugifrons. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1951
title: Anapausa rugifrons
